[
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hey Carlos, any word on that Telecaster neck reset? Been about two weeks since I dropped it off.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-04T06:00:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:25+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "It's done. Finished shaping the heel and got the action where it needs to be — plays clean all the way up the board now. Come by the workshop after 2:30, I'm running a charter out of Bayport til early afternoon.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-14T13:07:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:26+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002BILLY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Perfect. You think Thursday works? I've got a gig Friday night at the Elks lodge.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-26T13:19:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Thursday's fine. Granddaughter Elise is here through the weekend so I might be a little distracted but the guitar'll be ready.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-13T06:00:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002BILLY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha no worries, how old is she now?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-07T12:18:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:29+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Just turned 6. Already trying to tune my parlor guitar by ear. Mostly wrong but she's got the instinct.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-12T08:26:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:30+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002BILLY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "That's how it starts lol. What do I owe you on the reset?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-07T12:54:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:31+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Eighty-five. I had to recut the saddle too, didn't charge extra. Cash or Venmo, either works.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-07T09:39:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-29T11:33:32+00:00",
    "user_id": "U002BILLY"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Pete — tarpon are stacking up off Three Sisters Shoal. You still confirmed for the 5th?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-18T17:35:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:43:56+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hell yeah I'm confirmed. How many you seeing out there?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-23T13:43:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:43:57+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003PETE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Dozen rolls inside the channel before 7 this morning. Water's 86 and clear. Bring 80lb fluorocarbon leader, don't skip it.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-05T07:37:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:43:58+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Same departure time? 5 AM at the Bayport ramp?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-06T14:32:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:43:59+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003PETE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "5 AM. Luc's mateing for me that day — been out with me since Tuesday, he's getting sharp.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-09T08:14:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:44:00+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Nice, how's he doing out there?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-06T14:32:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:44:01+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003PETE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Better than me at netting. Don't tell him that.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-12T14:20:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:44:02+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha! Deal. Any chance I can bring my buddy Ray? He's never fished the Gulf. Pays his own way.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-13T06:24:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T03:44:03+00:00",
    "user_id": "U003PETE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Carlos, Luc texted me — says he's driving down from Tampa Saturday with Ashley and the kids. Wants to know if you're taking Elise and Beau out on the water or if that's too early for them.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-09T08:50:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:35+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Tide's at 6:40 Saturday, which is perfect. Told him dock by 5:30. Beau's old enough now, he'll be fine. Elise already knows how to hold a rod.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-11T07:13:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:36+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004ANDREA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "She really does lol. You want me to stock the bait well Friday night? Live shrimp or cut mullet?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-06T17:47:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:37+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Live shrimp. Beau loses patience fast — need the bite to stay hot or I'll be hearing about it the whole ride back.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-06T08:02:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:38+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004ANDREA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha. Fair warning, Mrs. Kellerman stopped by the shop this morning. Left that old parlor guitar — said the action's been cutting into her fingers for months.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-18T17:11:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:39+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "I saw it on the bench. Nut's sitting way too high, someone shimmed it with a matchbook at some point. Takes about ten minutes to fix if you have bone stock.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-07T09:39:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:40+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004ANDREA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "She's asking if it'll be done before the 4th. I told her I'd check with you.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-19T06:36:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:41+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Tell her Wednesday. And tell her whoever shimmed that nut with a matchbook owes her a proper repair, because that's not something that happens by accident. 🎸",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-26T07:37:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-27T17:49:42+00:00",
    "user_id": "U004ANDREA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Picked up a set of Engelmann spruce tops at the Tampa wood show yesterday — gorgeous figuring, just enough flex. Think I found the soundboard for that OM I'm building Luc for Christmas.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-04T09:15:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:24+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Oh nice, he know about it?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-15T11:29:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:25+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005DAVID"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Hell no. That's the point. Diane already almost blew it last Thanksgiving asking him what guitar size he plays. Woman cannot keep a secret to save her life 😄",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-21T08:14:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:26+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Ha! She mean well though. What bracing you running on it — scalloped X?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-03-24T08:14:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:27+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005DAVID"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Yeah, scalloped X, shifted back about a quarter inch. Tried that on the last dreadnought and it opened up real nice. Low end stayed tight.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-26T16:34:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:28+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "You brace it yourself or you sending it out?",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-13T09:27:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:29+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005DAVID"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Always do it myself. Sending it out defeats the whole thing. Luc's gonna play that guitar for 40 years, I want my hands on every part of it.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-02-05T16:58:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:30+00:00",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "general",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "That's a hell of a gift man. Elise and Beau are lucky too — kids growing up with a grandpa who builds guitars. Some things you just can't buy.",
    "thread_ts": "2026-01-01T06:48:00-04:00",
    "ts": "2026-03-28T06:42:31+00:00",
    "user_id": "U005DAVID"
  },
